modShortDescription: Modifies the Worldglobal.xml to reduce the moonlight ambiance, make it darker indoors and increase the day and night fog global effect.
modDescription:
Modifies the Worldglobal.xml to reduce the moonlight ambiance, make it darker indoors and increase the day and night [fog](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-weather/) global effect. The aim is to increase each subtly.

**[Download](https://docs.google.com/uc?export=download&id=1MkthWvknv_0h_4uIQKjGACQtWL-gMb3A)**

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/22900-sinicals-mods/).

**Credits:** [SiNiCaL](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/sinical/)
